2007-05-19  Benoît Dejean  <benoit@placenet.org>

	* features.def:
	* include/glibtop/proclist.h:

	Small API change.
	get_proclist returns pid_t instead of unsigned for consistency.
	I have checked many archs and this doesn't break the ABI.

